": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-de0a48973c737e0421a8648da9342a5a_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "86 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/523452874"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5d7NwanzxMYhEAMaCDc4NjA0MzExIJ+U5pEGMAE41gFADXIJNTIzNDUyODc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1685455642.7850766", "card_id": "Q_603823460", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "河南紧急下拨 2 亿元，专项用于小麦烘干，全省小麦目前收获 4.52%，这意味着什么？将产生哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据河南日报，5 月 30 日，经河南省政府专题研究决定，省财政紧急下拨资金 2 亿元，专项用于小麦烘干，确保小麦质量、确保颗粒归仓、确保农民收益。而河南省委农办发出通知，要求各地配合做好 2023 年小麦保险理赔。 另外，近十年来最严重「烂场雨」基本结束，河南全省小麦目前收获 4.52%。未来 5 天，河南全省大部以多云或晴天为主，仅西部地区有弱降水。紧急下拨 2 亿元，用于小麦烘干！河南遭遇 10 年来最严重「烂场雨」，小麦倒伏、发霉、发芽… | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-71b45913cf1bdc365efd91bf97902669_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603823460"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I5d7NwanzxMYhEAMaCDk2NDYzMzY2IPe11qMGMAA4GEAOcgk2MDM4MjM0NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1685455642.7858188", "card_id": "Q_600477983", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 351}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "和男朋友一年多，能力上没法帮助我，也不能提供很多情绪价值，交往还有意义吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "和男朋友在一起一年多，同城异地，周末见面，所以感觉交往很不生活，一年多进展较慢。 我们同一类工作，他研究生比我晚工作三年，平常在工作上我帮助他多一点。有时我也会跟他抱怨工作或说说比较麻烦的事，他会比较简短地回应，但给人的感觉就是复述事实。既没有帮我出谋划策，也没有对我比较消极的情绪进行回应。 我不是一定要他帮我做什么，我只是觉得一段恋情要么建立在生活情趣中（我们只能周末见面）；要么能对我有一定的引领和成长（慕强可能是绝大多数女生的本性）；要么能提供情绪价值。可是在平常的聊天中，我并不怎么能感觉到他对我情绪的重视或者是反馈，或者说，我感受不到他对我的在意和爱意。周末见面相处还好，可是周内在微信聊天的过程中，我会一遍遍陷入情绪的内耗。就会自我怀疑，这样的交往还有意义吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-b8a45aad1688517313d397b39966b19c_1440w.webp?source=6a64a727"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/600477983"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI5d7NwanzxMYhEAMaCDk1NzIwMDYzIK+Q9KIGMC04oQZAD3IJNjAwNDc3OTgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1685455642.7866402", "card_id": "Q_457212453", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "搞科研的你一般在什么情况 / 条件下最容易产生灵感？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在楼下散步，产生了不少好的科研点子，遂察觉夜间独自散步是我的灵感高发期。 认识的人里，有人的灵感高发期是洗澡的时候，还有和朋友喝酒的时候，想知道大家的灵感高发期都是怎样的条件？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-47e4bb4f1263b7b52301105dc42783b9_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457212453"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5d7NwanzxMYhEAMaCDYzODgyODY2ILqnq4QGMAE4kwFAEHIJNDU3MjEyNDUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1685455642.7872674", "card_id": "Q_602238086", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 98}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "安卓已经进入 16G 时代，为什么 iPhone14 系列运行内存最大只有 6G ？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-46fd6dc70cf0b99de13845f1c28a931b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color"